## Idea

Just as [[pretriangulated dg-categories]] are a model for [[stable (âˆž,1)-categories|stable]] [[linear (âˆž,1)-categories]] in the setting of [[dg-categories]], _pretriangulated $A_\infty$-categories_ are designed to be a model for [[stable (âˆž,1)-categories|stable]] [[linear (âˆž,1)-categories]] in the setting of $A_\infty$-[[A-âˆž-categories|categories]].

## References

* Yuri Bespalov, Volodymyr Lyubashenko, Oleksandr Manzyuk, _Pretriangulated $A_\infty$-categories_, Proceedings of the Institute of Mathematics of NAS of Ukraine, vol. 76, Institute of Mathematics of NAS of Ukraine, Kyiv, 2008, 599 p., [pdf](http://www.math.ksu.edu/~lub/cmcMonad.pdf).

